data.description: Get away from it all & experience the tranquility of nature in the foothills of the Big Belt Mountains. Exquisitely situated & masterfully crafted log home & separate log shop sit in the middle of the fenced 160 +/- acres bordering public land. Arriving at The Landing Zone Ranch you get the feeling of being in a natural oasis of privacy and dramatic mountain views. The hand hewn log home has soaring timber framed ceilings & a great room flanked by a master suite & loft on one side and second bedroom & loft on the other side. Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & moveable bar. Access the full length Trex deck from each of the bedrooms & great room thru beautiful patio doors. Radon: Well Log Available Get away from it all & experience the tranquility of nature in the foothills of the Big Belt Mountains. Exquisitely situated & masterfully crafted log home & separate log shop sit in the middle of the fenced 160 +/- acres bordering public land. Arriving at The Landing Zone Ranch you get the feeling of being in a natural oasis of privacy and dramatic mountain views. The hand hewn log home has soaring timber framed ceilings & a great room flanked by a master suite & loft on one side and second bedroom & loft on the other side. Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & moveable bar. Access the full length Trex deck from each of the bedrooms & great room thru beautiful patio doors. Full walk-out lower level with bedroom suite, gun vault, a multi-purpose room, mechanical room and family room. Six car detached heated log shop with drive-thru doors and guest apt. Springs and pond with water rights. Reputable hunting area with extraordinary wildlife populations.
